Installation Instructions
-------------------------

AFF4 uses the Scons build system which is already shipped with the
AFF4 source tree. To install:

1. Configure the package by editing the values in `./config.py'

2. Optionally type './scons' to compile the package.

3. Type './scons install' to install the libarary and programs and
   any data files and documentation. This will also compile the package
   if not already.

To uninstall.

1. Type `./scons -c install' to uninstall the library and programs and remove
   any data files and documentation.
